      <Meanings>
        <Meaning id="6b0a60d1-123a-4ded-ae15-e58475474323" type="Adjective">
          <Vi>vui vẻ, hân hoan, rộn ràng</Vi>
          <En>feeling or causing happiness and enjoyment; cheerful and lively.</En>
          <Example>She was in a merry mood and started singing and dancing.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="bd9fb3ab-5956-4a84-8df1-4cb9d6d7a4fb">
              <Vi>Mô tả trạng thái tinh thần vui vẻ, phấn chấn trong một buổi tiệc hoặc dịp lễ hội.</Vi>
              <En>Describing a cheerful and joyful emotional state, especially during a party or festive occasion.</En>
            </Situation>
            <Situation id="6acfba82-9c6a-429a-acc9-ecfc5722a098">
              <Vi>Dùng trong cụm từ “Merry Christmas” để chúc mừng Giáng sinh.</Vi>
              <En>Used in the phrase “Merry Christmas” to wish someone a joyful holiday.</En>
            </Situation>
